Standards-Version: 3.9.8
Homepage: https://www.nifty-networks.net/swirc/

Package: swirc
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: IRC client written with the Ncurses UI framework
 Swirc is a BSD licensed, console based and lightweight IRC client
 written in C and C++, whose goals are to be portable and secure.
 .
 Features:
  * TLS/SSL
  * Multiple IRCv3 features such as SASL auth mechanism
  * Themes
  * And more...
